(So I'll do it my way.)

24
00:01:05,275 --> 00:01:08,575
(I don't know whom I should get to know more now.)

25
00:01:09,845 --> 00:01:11,414
(Or just Si Won?)

26
00:01:11,415 --> 00:01:12,645
Or just Si Won?

27
00:01:14,555 --> 00:01:15,555
