42
00:02:05,205 --> 00:02:08,175
(I was hoping Ju Hee wouldn't win.)

43
00:02:08,835 --> 00:02:11,405
(She looked as if she was interested in another guy other than me.)

44
00:02:11,605 --> 00:02:15,915
(What's the huge benefit that will be given to Ju Hee and Yun So?)

45
00:02:16,115 --> 00:02:17,144
Last week,

46
00:02:17,145 --> 00:02:18,885
- they had a pool party together.
- Yes.

47
00:02:18,945 --> 00:02:20,284
- It was absolutely wild.
- Yes, it was.

48
00:02:20,285 --> 00:02:21,285
- Yes.
- Yes.

49
00:02:21,286 --> 00:02:22,654
Online communities are going wild...

50
00:02:22,655 --> 00:02:24,824
