60
00:02:42,135 --> 00:02:43,404
Even women...

61
00:02:43,405 --> 00:02:44,675
- appeared in the comments.
- Is that so?

62
00:02:44,875 --> 00:02:47,215
They're having a bloody battle over her.

63
00:02:47,575 --> 00:02:50,085
The romantic dynamics has shifted,

64
00:02:50,445 --> 00:02:53,255
