65
00:02:53,355 --> 00:02:54,654
Depending on how hard one works,

66
00:02:54,655 --> 00:02:55,684
- the dynamics can change.
- That's right.

67
00:02:55,685 --> 00:02:57,554
- This is their chance.
- Things can change...

68
00:02:57,555 --> 00:02:58,685
