77
00:03:25,815 --> 00:03:26,854
- Is that so?
- Yes.

78
00:03:26,855 --> 00:03:28,385
- You have to wait and see more?
- Yes.

79
00:03:28,915 --> 00:03:30,155
At first,

80
00:03:31,485 --> 00:03:33,995
