- Oh, no.

102
00:04:40,295 --> 00:04:41,395
Actually,

103
00:04:42,155 --> 00:04:43,865
I get Si Won...

104
00:04:43,995 --> 00:04:46,794
because Ji Seung didn't send her Love QR message to Si Won...

105
