but to Jun Han.

106
00:04:48,635 --> 00:04:50,234
Then it's natural for him to think...

107
00:04:50,235 --> 00:04:52,434
- that she lost feelings for him.
- Her interest... Right.

108
00:04:52,435 --> 00:04:54,874
And Yu Jin is showing interest in him,

109
00:04:54,875 --> 00:04:56,945
