117
00:05:16,595 --> 00:05:19,995
I had a date with Yu Jin, but I didn't choose her.

118
00:05:20,095 --> 00:05:22,365
But I flirted with her a bit while we were on a date.

119
00:05:23,505 --> 00:05:24,905
That's where it took a turn.

120
00:05:26,465 --> 00:05:28,874
I flirted with her, but I didn't send the Love QR message,

121
00:05:28,875 --> 00:05:30,275
