135
00:06:10,445 --> 00:06:12,045
- Yes.
- I did talk a lot with Ji Hye.

136
00:06:12,615 --> 00:06:15,115
But I talked a lot with Ji Hye yesterday, so...

137
00:06:15,515 --> 00:06:16,584
