143
00:06:29,395 --> 00:06:32,365
The day ended with us traveling back and forth.

144
00:06:32,805 --> 00:06:33,935
You're right.

145
00:06:36,105 --> 00:06:38,505
I felt a little unsettled.

146
00:06:39,345 --> 00:06:40,575
So I...

147
00:06:41,175 --> 00:06:44,314
(Last night, Jun Han heard Jin Young talk about Jeong Won.)

148
00:06:44,315 --> 00:06:49,485
(Last night, Jun Han heard Jin Young talk about Jeong Won.)

149
00:06:49,955 --> 00:06:53,525
I think Jeong Won and I...

150
00:06:53,725 --> 00:06:56,355
