167
00:07:37,035 --> 00:07:38,504
Shall we unpack those?

168
00:07:38,505 --> 00:07:40,004
- Unpack...
- Yes, let's unpack them.

169
00:07:40,005 --> 00:07:42,105
(Si Won is worried about Yu Jin who isn't in good condition.)

170
00:07:43,235 --> 00:07:44,345
