186
00:08:24,745 --> 00:08:27,885
Why would he... Why on earth...

187
00:08:28,555 --> 00:08:31,954
So I want to talk with Jun Han soon.

188
00:08:31,955 --> 00:08:33,285
I want to know how he feels.

189
00:08:37,295 --> 00:08:39,624
They should have a talk together.

190
00:08:39,625 --> 00:08:40,895
