217
00:09:34,715 --> 00:09:35,954
- Should I put something on my face?
- Let me see.

218
00:09:35,955 --> 00:09:37,185
Don't you have something on your face?

219
00:09:37,285 --> 00:09:38,454
- Hold on.
- I think you have something...

220
00:09:38,455 --> 00:09:39,584
on your face.

221
00:09:39,585 --> 00:09:40,825
(Applying)

222
00:09:41,225 --> 00:09:43,825
Oh, my.

223
00:09:48,295 --> 00:09:49,994
We should have porridge next time.

224
00:09:49,995 --> 00:09:51,005
- Right?
- Yes.

225
00:09:51,335 --> 00:09:52,604
I think I just need to sleep.

226
00:09:52,605 --> 00:09:54,275
I'll be okay after I get a lot of sleep.

227
00:09:54,535 --> 00:09:56,075
