233
00:10:07,015 --> 00:10:08,814
That must be why you're in such bad condition.

234
00:10:08,815 --> 00:10:09,854
- Sorry?
- That must be why...

235
00:10:09,855 --> 00:10:10,855
you're in such bad condition.

236
00:10:10,856 --> 00:10:12,685
(Si Won can't stop worrying about Yu Jin who isn't well.)

237
00:10:13,995 --> 00:10:15,724
