242
00:10:22,335 --> 00:10:24,064
I see.

243
00:10:24,065 --> 00:10:25,435
- Half and half?
- Half and half?

244
00:10:26,905 --> 00:10:27,934
Yes.

245
00:10:27,935 --> 00:10:29,235
