251
00:10:42,215 --> 00:10:43,515
Someone she showed interest in?

252
00:10:44,455 --> 00:10:45,685
Someone she showed her interest in in her own way.

253
00:10:45,885 --> 00:10:47,695
Show interest in my own way?

254
00:10:48,255 --> 00:10:50,094
- You couldn't tell?
- No.

255
