257
00:10:56,395 --> 00:10:57,405
Maybe not?

258
00:10:58,035 --> 00:10:59,235
- You could have.
- Maybe I didn't.

259
00:11:01,535 --> 00:11:05,145
(Jeong Won and Jin Young leave the table for a second.)

260
00:11:05,575 --> 00:11:07,245
- Is it Jeong Won?
- What do you mean?

261
00:11:09,245 --> 00:11:10,245
Someone you showed your interest in obviously.

262
00:11:10,515 --> 00:11:11,715
Didn't it show?

263
00:11:12,215 --> 00:11:14,015
- I wasn't sure.
- I see.

264
00:11:16,615 --> 00:11:17,985
I thought I showed it.

265
00:11:19,555 --> 00:11:20,555
In my own way.

266
00:11:20,556 --> 00:11:22,324
(Thinking)

267
00:11:22,325 --> 00:11:24,664
But we don't make it so obvious.

268
00:11:24,665 --> 00:11:26,025
(Wary)

269
00:11:26,425 --> 00:11:30,705
(A night that makes you want to know how they truly feel)

270
00:11:31,405 --> 00:11:35,304
(The older women and younger men gather outside after dinner.)

271
00:11:35,305 --> 00:11:36,535
I think it's going to be a bit cold.

272
00:11:38,575 --> 00:11:39,575
Yes, I'm the first to be here.

273
00:11:39,745 --> 00:11:41,814
He took the seat next to her.

274
00:11:41,815 --> 00:11:43,014
Do you want another jacket?

275
00:11:43,015 --> 00:11:44,144
Later when it gets colder.

276
00:11:44,145 --> 00:11:45,915
(Jin Wu quickly took the seat next to Ji Hye.)

277
00:11:46,215 --> 00:11:50,655
(Jeong Won's seat is a little far from Ji Hye's.)

278
00:11:51,055 --> 00:11:52,224
(Jun Han quickly sits next to Jin Young.)

279
00:11:52,225 --> 00:11:53,255
Here.

280
00:11:55,255 --> 00:11:57,264
- Take this.
- Thank you.

281
00:11:57,265 --> 00:11:59,625
(Ji Seung and Si Won are sitting next to each other.)

282
00:12:00,165 --> 00:12:02,934
(Ju Hee is looking for an empty seat across from Yun So.)

283
00:12:02,935 --> 00:12:04,104
- No.
- What?

284
00:12:04,105 --> 00:12:06,165
- Can I sit there?
- Yes.

285
00:12:06,335 --> 00:12:08,135
- Can I sit there?
- Yes.

286
00:12:08,305 --> 00:12:09,734
Please switch seats with me.

287
00:12:09,735 --> 00:12:11,144
I'll sit there.

288
00:12:11,145 --> 00:12:13,545
No. Stop, Yun So.

289
00:12:15,115 --> 00:12:18,744
(Yun So takes the seat next to Ju Hee.)

290
00:12:18,745 --> 00:12:20,084
- There's a hand warmer?
- It's so warm.

291
00:12:20,085 --> 00:12:21,515
(Looking)

292
00:12:22,315 --> 00:12:24,955
- Oh, no.
- She doesn't like it.

293
00:12:25,385 --> 00:12:27,085
(Looking)

294
00:12:28,425 --> 00:12:30,895
Did you want to switch seats because...

295
00:12:31,095 --> 00:12:32,265
You're right.

296
00:12:32,765 --> 00:12:33,865
That's awesome.

297
00:12:34,595 --> 00:12:35,634
He's awesome.

298
00:12:35,635 --> 00:12:37,734
(Unlike his confident answer, he can't look at Ju Hee.)

299
00:12:37,735 --> 00:12:38,904
I know. It's hot.

300
00:12:38,905 --> 00:12:40,674
- You must be cold.
- I'm not.

301
00:12:40,675 --> 00:12:43,435
(Ju Hee doesn't make eye contact with Yun So either.)

302
00:12:44,005 --> 00:12:49,114
(The dynamic between them has clearly changed.)

303
00:12:49,115 --> 00:12:51,184
Honestly, I didn't know...

304
00:12:51,185 --> 00:12:53,584
Ju Hee was this cold.

305
00:12:53,585 --> 00:12:55,754
She wants to get to know different people there.

306
00:12:55,755 --> 00:12:57,014
- Yes, and talk with them.
- So she feels uncomfortable...

307
00:12:57,015 --> 00:12:58,285
to be paired up with just one person.

308
00:12:58,325 --> 00:13:01,394
But for Yun So, there's too little time,

309
00:13:01,395 --> 00:13:03,425
so he can't lose her.

310
00:13:03,755 --> 00:13:05,464
He should've kept a little distance...

311
00:13:05,465 --> 00:13:06,864
and expressed that he still is...

312
00:13:06,865 --> 00:13:08,234
- interested in her.
- Right.

313
00:13:08,235 --> 00:13:10,465
But he wouldn't give her that chance.

314
00:13:11,235 --> 00:13:12,435
This is bad.

315
00:13:12,705 --> 00:13:14,305
Something you can't tolerate.

316
00:13:16,005 --> 00:13:17,035
We got a message.

317
00:13:18,645 --> 00:13:19,775
(Surprised)

318
00:13:20,305 --> 00:13:22,114
(What does the message say?)

319
00:13:22,115 --> 00:13:23,775
What? Is it about the benefit?

320
00:13:24,315 --> 00:13:26,585
- Truth Card.
- What?

321
00:13:27,585 --> 00:13:30,724
(Truth Game that lets you get a glimpse of your crush's feelings)

322
00:13:30,725 --> 00:13:31,785
It's the Truth Game.

323
00:13:33,655 --> 00:13:35,094
(Pick a Truth Card and answer it. No skipping questions.)

324
00:13:35,095 --> 00:13:36,394
We can't refuse to answer.

325
00:13:36,395 --> 00:13:37,694
We can't skip the questions either.

326
00:13:37,695 --> 00:13:39,224
- Oh, no.
- We can't refuse either.

327
00:13:39,225 --> 00:13:40,564
This is a real Truth Game.

328
00:13:40,565 --> 00:13:41,734
It really is a Truth Game.

329
00:13:41,735 --> 00:13:42,735
It'll be fun.

330
00:13:43,595 --> 00:13:44,835
My heart is suddenly beating fast.

331
00:13:47,435 --> 00:13:49,874
(A turning point where new relationships may begin...)

332
00:13:49,875 --> 00:13:54,174
(and old ones may come to an end)

333
00:13:54,175 --> 00:13:56,274
- I'll go first.
- Sounds good.

334
00:13:56,275 --> 00:13:57,785
(The Truth Game starts with Yu Jin.)

335
00:13:59,015 --> 00:14:01,614
- There's a lot.
- Oh, please!

336
00:14:01,615 --> 00:14:03,485
Please let me get a safe one.

337
00:14:04,955 --> 00:14:05,955
Please...

338
00:14:05,956 --> 00:14:07,454
You should read the question for us.

339
00:14:07,455 --> 00:14:08,695
Put it in front for us.

340
00:14:09,455 --> 00:14:10,554
It's going to be fun.

341
00:14:10,555 --> 00:14:11,625
(Curious)

342
00:14:16,835 --> 00:14:18,035
- What is it?
- What is it?

343
00:14:18,135 --> 00:14:20,264
- What is it?
- What is it? Hurry up and read it.

344
00:14:20,265 --> 00:14:21,434
- What is it?
- It must be intense.

345
00:14:21,435 --> 00:14:23,105
- Read it for us.
- Why? Is it bold?

346
00:14:23,235 --> 00:14:24,904
- It must be bold.
- What is it?

347
00:14:24,905 --> 00:14:28,274
- I'm so curious.
- Must I reveal the question?

348
00:14:28,275 --> 00:14:29,814
- Of course.
- You should reveal it...

349
00:14:29,815 --> 00:14:31,344
so we'd know what it is.

350
00:14:31,345 --> 00:14:32,644
You need to reveal it so we'd know.

351
00:14:32,645 --> 00:14:34,415
- Let's go.
- This is fun.

352
00:14:35,055 --> 00:14:39,484
"Draw a heart on the palm of the person..."

353
00:14:39,485 --> 00:14:41,325
"that was most charming today."

354
00:14:44,165 --> 00:14:45,964
This will openly show...

355
00:14:45,965 --> 00:14:47,295
where her heart is headed.

356
00:14:47,695 --> 00:14:49,294
- How do you draw a heart?
- A heart on the palm.

357
00:14:49,295 --> 00:14:50,635
Oh, like this?

358
00:14:51,165 --> 00:14:52,635
This is so intense.

359
00:14:54,935 --> 00:14:57,005
Why did I volunteer to go first?

360
00:14:58,975 --> 00:15:00,175
This is making me more nervous.

361
00:15:02,245 --> 00:15:03,345
I'll take a lap first.

362
00:15:04,245 --> 00:15:06,385
- Is this Duck, Duck, Goose?
- I'm too nervous to do it.

363
00:15:07,755 --> 00:15:12,054
(Curious, excited)

364
00:15:12,055 --> 00:15:13,225
What is this?

365
00:15:13,255 --> 00:15:14,654
You really can't tell.

366
00:15:14,655 --> 00:15:15,724
(Which younger man captured Yu Jin's heart today?)

367
00:15:15,725 --> 00:15:17,155
Why did I volunteer to go first?

368
00:15:17,425 --> 00:15:19,425
Going first is a bit hard.

369
00:15:20,625 --> 00:15:21,994
This is fun!

370
00:15:21,995 --> 00:15:23,095
(Yu Jin chose Si Won.)

371
00:15:25,565 --> 00:15:27,875
(Shy)

372
00:15:30,535 --> 00:15:32,474
(That's so sweet.)

373
00:15:32,475 --> 00:15:35,745
Just play it. Cut the scene to Ji Seung!

374
00:15:36,015 --> 00:15:38,814
The one to do it must be really nervous.

375
00:15:38,815 --> 00:15:39,815
This is intense.

376
00:15:42,655 --> 00:15:43,784
That's it!

377
00:15:43,785 --> 00:15:44,824
(She really can't keep a straight face.)

378
00:15:44,825 --> 00:15:46,155
Ji Seung completely gave herself away.

379
00:15:48,025 --> 00:15:50,694
I'm so nervous. Oh, my.

380
00:15:50,695 --> 00:15:51,695
This is crazy.

381
00:15:52,825 --> 00:15:54,195
I think she's really attractive.

382
00:15:54,795 --> 00:15:57,435
I was so embarrassed that I thought my head would explode.

383
00:15:58,165 --> 00:16:01,505
As for Si Won... At the pool...

384
00:16:02,635 --> 00:16:05,174
(Si Won blocked the waves that were crashing in.)

385
00:16:05,175 --> 00:16:06,845
I couldn't help but look at him.

386
00:16:07,545 --> 00:16:11,245
When they played the game, he looked really cool.

387
00:16:11,615 --> 00:16:12,945
He seemed competitive too.

388
00:16:13,545 --> 00:16:16,184
I thought, "He's so cool."

389
00:16:16,185 --> 00:16:18,425
(He's so cool.)

390
00:16:18,925 --> 00:16:20,124
Let's go.

391
00:16:20,125 --> 00:16:22,954
(Jeong Won is the second to go.)

392
00:16:22,955 --> 00:16:24,995
You must pick the one at the very front or the very back.

393
00:16:28,265 --> 00:16:29,395
Darn!

394
00:16:29,465 --> 00:16:31,265
- What is it?
- Why?

395
00:16:31,335 --> 00:16:33,705
What is it? I'm scared.

396
00:16:34,075 --> 00:16:35,835
- It must be a really bold one.
- Why?

397
00:16:36,775 --> 00:16:38,704
I'm so curious that I feel dizzy. Hurry up and read it for us.

398
00:16:38,705 --> 00:16:39,744
What is it?

399
00:16:39,745 --> 00:16:41,015
- Just read it first.
- Read it for us.

400
00:16:41,115 --> 00:16:43,875
"A sweet confession for the person you're most interested in."

401
00:16:45,685 --> 00:16:48,455
You have to openly choose one.

402
00:16:48,615 --> 00:16:51,485
- This isn't easy.
- The questions are really intense.

403
00:16:51,625 --> 00:16:55,454
I have to do it to the person I'm most interested in now.

404
00:16:55,455 --> 00:16:56,854
That's right.

405
00:16:56,855 --> 00:16:58,724
So it shouldn't pressure you much.

406
00:16:58,725 --> 00:16:59,894
But it is pressuring.

407
00:16:59,895 --> 00:17:02,764
Your feelings can change anytime.

408
00:17:02,765 --> 00:17:04,135
That's right.

409
00:17:05,435 --> 00:17:06,465
It's really intense.

410
00:17:07,365 --> 00:17:10,435
(Who is Jeong Won most interested in?)

411
00:17:10,705 --> 00:17:14,115
(Ji Hye whom he was with the whole day?)

412
00:17:14,315 --> 00:17:15,315
(Jin Young whom he promised a date with?)

413
00:17:15,316 --> 00:17:16,415
Who could it be?

414
00:17:18,815 --> 00:17:20,544
(Who will Jeong Won choose?)

415
00:17:20,545 --> 00:17:22,314
Okay.

416
00:17:22,315 --> 00:17:23,315
(Turning)

417
00:17:23,316 --> 00:17:26,485
I had a really great time again today.

418
00:17:29,995 --> 00:17:30,995
So manly.

419
00:17:30,996 --> 00:17:33,025
Gosh, you're so manly.

420
00:17:37,965 --> 00:17:39,964
- Isn't a cynical smirk...
- That's it.

421
00:17:39,965 --> 00:17:41,405
rather better?

422
00:17:41,535 --> 00:17:44,575
To make this more fun, we should cut to Ji Seung now.

423
00:17:44,645 --> 00:17:46,405
If Ji Seung is smiling...

424
00:17:46,845 --> 00:17:48,645
Cut to her scene right away.

425
00:17:49,375 --> 00:17:51,884
(Smiling broadly)

426
00:17:51,885 --> 00:17:53,745
Seriously, what is this? What should I do?

427
00:17:53,985 --> 00:17:54,985
(Jeong Won chose Ji Hye as the one he's most interested in.)

428
00:17:54,986 --> 00:17:56,014
So manly.

429
00:17:56,015 --> 00:17:57,655
Gosh, you're so manly.

430
00:18:00,925 --> 00:18:02,925
(Relieved)

431
00:18:04,425 --> 00:18:06,125
This time, not just his ears...

432
00:18:07,635 --> 00:18:09,335
His face is getting red too.

433
00:18:10,935 --> 00:18:12,435
Gosh, Ji Hye is happy.

434
00:18:13,135 --> 00:18:14,204
(Ji Hye is the third to go.)

435
00:18:14,205 --> 00:18:15,235
Oh, well.

436
00:18:15,875 --> 00:18:17,574
- I really want a safe one.
- This is so intense.

437
00:18:17,575 --> 00:18:19,244
- Please!
- There's no safe question.

438
00:18:19,245 --> 00:18:21,245
- Please!
- This is bad. What do I do?

439
00:18:24,215 --> 00:18:26,585
Please. Seriously.

440
00:18:31,385 --> 00:18:32,885
I really don't have one for this.

441
00:18:34,195 --> 00:18:35,195
(What is Ji Hye's question?)

442
00:18:35,196 --> 00:18:36,725
He looks serious too.

443
00:18:41,035 --> 00:18:43,465
"What's the name of the person who makes you most confused?"

444
00:18:44,635 --> 00:18:46,135
Oh, you're not confused.

445
00:18:46,735 --> 00:18:48,175
I'm not.

446
00:18:51,875 --> 00:18:52,875
Then someone...

447
00:18:52,876 --> 00:18:54,574
I think we can tell even if you don't share.

448
00:18:54,575 --> 00:18:56,144
- Then what do we do?
- Then how about...

449
00:18:56,145 --> 00:18:57,685
adding "not" in front?

450
00:18:58,645 --> 00:19:00,715
"What's the name of the person who makes you not confused?"

451
00:19:00,955 --> 00:19:02,755
But this is so clear too.

452
00:19:04,185 --> 00:19:05,224
There's none.

453
00:19:05,225 --> 00:19:06,884
There's no one who makes me confused.

454
00:19:06,885 --> 00:19:08,095
Who could it be?

455
00:19:09,455 --> 00:19:10,595
These two.

456
00:19:10,625 --> 00:19:12,425
Gosh, Ji Hye is clear.

457
00:19:12,865 --> 00:19:15,535
I don't know. They could make me confused later. Who knows?

458
00:19:16,635 --> 00:19:17,704
You're right.

459
00:19:17,705 --> 00:19:20,305
- It's as of now.
- Yes, it's as of now.

460
00:19:21,005 --> 00:19:24,745
(What is Jin Wu's question?)

461
00:19:27,715 --> 00:19:29,075
"Is there anyone you had feelings for..."

462
00:19:29,815 --> 00:19:33,015
"but hid without expressing?"

463
00:19:41,895 --> 00:19:42,895
Never.

464
00:19:42,896 --> 00:19:44,965
(I've never hidden my feelings.)

465
00:19:45,765 --> 00:19:48,165
I've only expressed my feelings to the person I'm interested in.

466
00:19:54,575 --> 00:19:55,635
He's cool.

467
00:19:57,375 --> 00:19:59,604
Jin Wu is still certain.

468
00:19:59,605 --> 00:20:01,015
He's firm.

469
00:20:04,245 --> 00:20:07,854
(What is the question for Yun So?)

470
00:20:07,855 --> 00:20:09,555
It's the same question.

471
00:20:09,855 --> 00:20:10,914
"Make a heart-fluttering confession..."

472
00:20:10,915 --> 00:20:12,025
"to the person you're most interested in."

473
00:20:12,925 --> 00:20:14,795
- Just do it.
- You can just do it.

474
00:20:15,095 --> 00:20:16,294
Just do it.

475
00:20:16,295 --> 00:20:17,864
(A fluttering confession by straightforward Yun So?)

476
00:20:17,865 --> 00:20:19,225
Out of all questions.

477
00:20:20,695 --> 00:20:22,995
From the start until now,

478
00:20:23,195 --> 00:20:24,305
you're the only one for me.

479
00:20:25,035 --> 00:20:28,335
From the start until now, you're the only one for me.

480
00:20:28,875 --> 00:20:30,135
Goodness.

481
00:20:30,475 --> 00:20:32,545
- This is insane.
- You picked the right card.

482
00:20:34,475 --> 00:20:38,615
(Although she heard Yun So's sincere feelings...)

483
00:20:39,015 --> 00:20:40,814
Oh, dear.

484
00:20:40,815 --> 00:20:42,855
She doesn't seem to like it.

485
00:20:46,025 --> 00:20:50,655
(Yun So can't look Ju Hee in the eye too.)

486
00:20:50,795 --> 00:20:51,795
(What is Si Won's question?)

487
00:20:51,796 --> 00:20:53,325
Si Won, read your question.

488
00:20:53,695 --> 00:20:56,665
"Interested in two people? Up or down."

489
00:20:57,565 --> 00:20:59,465
This is pretty simple.

490
00:20:59,535 --> 00:21:01,304
It really is the most simple question.

491
00:21:01,305 --> 00:21:03,235
It's simple, yes.

492
00:21:04,405 --> 00:21:06,205
(Si Won thinks long and hard.)

493
00:21:06,405 --> 00:21:08,645
(Glancing)

494
00:21:09,375 --> 00:21:10,615
Up for me.

495
00:21:11,745 --> 00:21:14,014
You're interested in two or more people?

496
00:21:14,015 --> 00:21:15,285
Two or more.

497
00:21:15,385 --> 00:21:16,684
- More?
- Two or more.

498
00:21:16,685 --> 00:21:18,384
(He's interested in two or more older women.)

499
00:21:18,385 --> 00:21:20,255
(Glancing)

500
00:21:25,795 --> 00:21:29,565
Initially, I wanted to get to know Ji Seung better.

501
00:21:30,565 --> 00:21:33,935
But she sent her Love QR to someone else yesterday.

502
00:21:35,435 --> 00:21:39,145
That made me think, "I should get to know more..."

503
00:21:39,245 --> 00:21:41,215
"about someone else too."

504
00:21:41,475 --> 00:21:43,645
That's why I answered as such.

505
00:21:44,745 --> 00:21:46,815
(Ji Seung's question?)

506
00:21:48,355 --> 00:21:49,814
"Did your feelings..."

507
00:21:49,815 --> 00:21:52,155
"ever waver today? Yes or no?"

508
00:21:52,655 --> 00:21:54,394
(On the first day, Ji Seung voted for Si Won...)

509
00:21:54,395 --> 00:21:56,095
(for the best first impression.)

510
00:21:57,025 --> 00:21:58,164
She did.

511
00:21:58,165 --> 00:21:59,395
(Jun Han received a Love QR from Ji Seung last night.)

512
00:21:59,665 --> 00:22:03,595
(Did Ji Seung's feelings waver?)

513
00:22:04,365 --> 00:22:05,505
No.

514
00:22:06,165 --> 00:22:07,235
No.

515
00:22:07,365 --> 00:22:08,504
- What?
- What?

516
00:22:08,505 --> 00:22:10,405
(Si Won looks puzzled.)

517
00:22:11,605 --> 00:22:13,545
Ji Seung is...

518
00:22:14,245 --> 00:22:15,844
I can't tell...

519
00:22:15,845 --> 00:22:17,815
what Ji Seung is thinking.

520
00:22:18,715 --> 00:22:20,285
- Me too.
- I can't tell.

521
00:22:21,715 --> 00:22:23,384
Ji Seung...

522
00:22:23,385 --> 00:22:25,855
I don't know what she's thinking.

523
00:22:27,385 --> 00:22:33,025
(Who does Ji Seung have feelings for?)

524
00:22:33,695 --> 00:22:35,664
Si Won was the only one for me.

525
00:22:35,665 --> 00:22:36,994
There was no alternative.

526
00:22:36,995 --> 00:22:38,105
What?

