00:47:46,983 --> 00:47:49,722
Right? She doesn't really feel the same.

1062
00:47:49,723 --> 00:47:50,853
That's why...

1063
00:47:50,983 --> 00:47:53,292
But who Yun So chose...

1064
00:47:53,293 --> 00:47:55,223
- went beyond my imagination.
- Really?

1065
00:47:55,463 --> 00:47:57,423
That means they're in a love square.

1066
00:47:57,593 --> 00:47:58,932
It's too tangled up.

1067
00:47:58,933 --> 00:48:00,333
(Yun So to Ju Hee to Jun Han to Jin Young)

1068
00:48:02,033 --> 00:48:03,333
This is crazy.

1069
00:48:03,863 --> 00:48:06,172
The rest of them don't know that Yun So...

1070
00:48:06,173 --> 00:48:07,572
has been rejected by Ju Hee.

1071
00:48:07,573 --> 00:48:08,743
No, they don't.

1072
00:48:10,573 --> 00:48:11,803
Now...

1073
00:48:12,173 --> 00:48:15,283
- The whole game has changed.
- The whole game has changed.

1074
00:48:15,843 --> 00:48:17,882
But we never know what'll happen after their overnight stay.

1075
00:48:17,883 --> 00:48:20,112
We really should play the Truth Game two days later.

1076
00:48:20,113 --> 00:48:22,083
We should.

1077
00:48:23,323 --> 00:48:24,382
- Interesting.
- Little did I know...

1078
00:48:24,383 --> 00:48:25,393
it'd be an overnight stay.

1079
00:48:28,493 --> 00:48:32,393
(A chaotic night of hidden feelings revealed)

1080
00:48:32,863 --> 00:48:35,062
(On their way to the overnight stay)

1081
00:48:35,063 --> 00:48:37,802
- Gosh.
- Man, my heart is pounding now.

1082
00:48:37,803 --> 00:48:39,403
(Yun So and Jin Young)

1083
00:48:39,433 --> 00:48:40,532
(Hesitating)

1084
00:48:40,533 --> 00:48:41,833
Where were we told to go?

1085
00:48:41,873 --> 00:48:43,243
Is it that place next door?

1086
00:48:43,673 --> 00:48:45,872
Look at the four.

1087
00:48:45,873 --> 00:48:47,213
(Jun Han and Ju Hee spot Yun So and Jin Young.)

1088
00:48:47,573 --> 00:48:48,742
Do we have to walk together?

1089
00:48:48,743 --> 00:48:49,743
Can we wait a bit?

1090
00:48:49,744 --> 00:48:50,782
- Let's do that.
- Cool.

1091
00:48:50,783 --> 00:48:52,383
- Why don't we hide over here?
- They're coming back.

1092
00:48:52,713 --> 00:48:53,882
Should we check out the guest room?

1093
00:48:53,883 --> 00:48:54,982
(Spotted Jun Han and Ju Hee)

1094
00:48:54,983 --> 00:48:56,482
Should we look at the room first?

1095
00:48:56,483 --> 00:48:57,822
- Okay.
- Good.

1096
00:48:57,823 --> 00:48:59,823
For real, my heart is pounding hard.

1097
00:49:00,523 --> 00:49:01,923
- I'm sorry.
- No.

1098
00:49:01,993 --> 00:49:03,963
I have a feeling I caused trouble.

1099
00:49:04,923 --> 00:49:07,233
What's worse, we share a room.

1100
00:49:07,463 --> 00:49:09,102
- Really?
- She's right.

1101
00:49:09,103 --> 00:49:11,202
(Coincidentally, Ju Hee and Jin Young are roommates.)

1102
00:49:11,203 --> 00:49:12,673
We share a room together.

1103
00:49:13,303 --> 00:49:14,873
To think he'd choose my roommate.

1104
00:49:15,503 --> 00:49:17,003
(Yawning)

1105
00:49:18,713 --> 00:49:21,072
Guys, the two are walking.

1106
00:49:21,073 --> 00:49:22,982
- Where?
- Where?

1107
00:49:22,983 --> 00:49:24,612
- Where are they going?
- And they're holding hands.

1108
00:49:24,613 --> 00:49:26,012
Where? And they're holding hands?

1109
00:49:26,013 --> 00:49:28,112
(Laughing hard)

1110
00:49:28,113 --> 00:49:30,323
Hold on. You stand out, Ji Hye.

1111
00:49:30,583 --> 00:49:31,823
It's too obvious.

1112
00:49:33,823 --> 00:49:35,892
They're walking past us while holding hands.

1113
00:49:35,893 --> 00:49:37,722
Where? And they're holding hands?

1114
00:49:37,723 --> 00:49:38,763
Maybe not.

1115
00:49:39,333 --> 00:49:42,263
Guys, you're clearly visible from the outside.

1116
00:49:42,403 --> 00:49:43,933
This is the last thing I expected.

1117
00:49:45,373 --> 00:49:46,503
I'm stunned.

1118
00:49:47,033 --> 00:49:48,533
Here they go.

1119
00:49:50,603 --> 00:49:51,802
- What?
- Oh, my.

1120
00:49:51,803 --> 00:49:53,072
That must be the guest room.

1121
00:49:53,073 --> 00:49:54,313
- No, that's our room.
- What?

1122
00:49:54,713 --> 00:49:56,083
That's our room.

1123
00:49:56,343 --> 00:49:57,712
Are they going over for his stuff?

1124
00:49:57,713 --> 00:49:59,752
- No, the two are going in together.
- Oh, my.

1125
00:49:59,753 --> 00:50:01,213
- Oh, my.
- Oh, gosh.

1126
00:50:01,813 --> 00:50:03,052
(Making a big fuss)

1127
00:50:03,053 --> 00:50:04,253
What's going on?

1128
00:50:04,783 --> 00:50:07,092
(The two came into Jun Han's room to avoid Yun So and Jin Young.)

1129
00:50:07,093 --> 00:50:11,423
It felt like you already had someone in mind.

1130
00:50:11,693 --> 00:50:13,763
So I took a long time to decide.

1131
00:50:14,133 --> 00:50:15,263
Take a seat.

1132
00:50:15,703 --> 00:50:16,963
- You mean Jin Young?
- Yes.

1133
00:50:18,333 --> 00:50:19,633
To be honest,

1134
00:50:20,033 --> 00:50:22,603
I was more curious about Jin Young.

1135
00:50:23,643 --> 00:50:25,372
I'm not a fan of people who confuse me.

1136
00:50:25,373 --> 00:50:26,373
I see.

1137
00:50:26,374 --> 00:50:27,973
But the answer she gave today...

1138
00:50:28,843 --> 00:50:31,413
disappointed me quite a bit.

1139
00:50:31,783 --> 00:50:33,352
You know how we sat...

1140
00:50:33,353 --> 00:50:36,383
diagonally from each other, and our eyes met a lot?

1141
00:50:37,023 --> 00:50:38,323
It made me feel...

1142
00:50:38,853 --> 00:50:40,052
a bit strange.

1143
00:50:40,053 --> 00:50:42,822
(It made me feel a bit strange!)

1144
00:50:42,823 --> 00:50:45,463
(Embarrassed)

1145
00:50:46,233 --> 00:50:49,103
Yesterday, the two talked in the chat room.

1146
00:50:49,163 --> 00:50:50,662
They're starting to talk a lot more.

1147
00:50:50,663 --> 00:50:52,203
(Jun Han and Ju Hee's eyes often met.)

1148
00:50:53,973 --> 00:50:56,343
I can hardly make eye contact with Jin Young.

1149
00:50:57,243 --> 00:50:59,613
But the two of us made...

1150
00:51:00,413 --> 00:51:02,143
eye contact quite a few times.

1151
00:51:03,483 --> 00:51:06,383
Do you prefer talking while making eye contact?

1152
00:51:06,953 --> 00:51:09,053
I like people whom I don't have to avoid looking at.

1153
00:51:10,123 --> 00:51:13,253
If I end up having to look away,

1154
00:51:13,593 --> 00:51:14,593
it makes me uncomfortable.

1155
00:51:14,594 --> 00:51:16,423
Same here.

1156
00:51:18,693 --> 00:51:19,993
Either way, I feel all shy.

1157
00:51:20,293 --> 00:51:21,992
Shall we go? We could go and...

1158
00:51:21,993 --> 00:51:23,462
- I'll see you off.
- After that...

1159
00:51:23,463 --> 00:51:25,732
- Let's meet again.
- We can talk more in that room.

1160
00:51:25,733 --> 00:51:27,802
(The guest room)

1161
00:51:27,803 --> 00:51:28,903
By the way,

1162
00:51:29,143 --> 00:51:30,643
- are you a light sleeper?
- What?

1163
00:51:31,703 --> 00:51:33,373
Not really.

1164
00:51:33,613 --> 00:51:35,483
- Is that so?
- And I brought this with me.

1165
00:51:35,683 --> 00:51:37,043
(Glancing)

1166
00:51:38,213 --> 00:51:39,653
- Oh, dear.
- Oh, gosh.

1167
00:51:40,253 --> 00:51:41,353
Hold on.

1168
00:51:41,853 --> 00:51:43,583
What terrible timing.

1169
00:51:44,123 --> 00:51:46,723
Won't it look bad if we keep avoiding him?

1170
00:51:46,753 --> 00:51:48,153
- Should we just make the trip?
- Yes.

1171
00:51:49,493 --> 00:51:50,822
Ju Hee wants to stop avoiding him.

1172
00:51:50,823 --> 00:51:52,692
How about coming over whenever you're done?

1173
00:51:52,693 --> 00:51:55,033
- Okay. I'll come over.
- Okay.

1174
00:51:55,463 --> 00:51:56,732
- See you later.
- Bye.

1175
00:51:56,733 --> 00:51:58,103
- I'll knock.
- Got it.

1176
00:51:59,003 --> 00:52:01,133
Pajamas.

1177
00:52:03,003 --> 00:52:04,942
Pajamas. She must be waiting.

1178
00:52:04,943 --> 00:52:06,073
(Jun Han looks excited.)

1179
00:52:06,343 --> 00:52:10,243
(Preparing a full bag for tonight)

1180
00:52:11,413 --> 00:52:13,213
I'm done. Yes.

1181
00:52:13,513 --> 00:52:14,683
Am I missing something?

1182
00:52:14,713 --> 00:52:16,522
He's nervous. Look at him talking to himself.

1183
00:52:16,523 --> 00:52:17,653
No, I'm not.

1184
00:52:17,923 --> 00:52:19,193
- Let's go.
- He's nervous.

1185
00:52:21,123 --> 00:52:22,393
Toothbrush, toothpaste...

1186
00:52:23,893 --> 00:52:25,093
Toiletries.

1187
00:52:26,133 --> 00:52:29,032
Underwear, swimsuit, change of clothes, and pajamas.

1188
00:52:29,033 --> 00:52:30,803
- Isn't the room next door?
- Yes.

1189
00:52:30,903 --> 00:52:32,103
He can just drop by again.

1190
00:52:32,603 --> 00:52:33,933
You're not going overseas.

1191
00:52:34,233 --> 00:52:36,103
(Knocking)

1192
00:52:40,143 --> 00:52:41,473
- Are you all set?
- Yes.

1193
00:52:42,683 --> 00:52:45,143
Why are you suddenly being all formal?

1194
00:52:45,443 --> 00:52:46,953
I'm nervous.

1195
00:52:49,053 --> 00:52:50,582
This must be the guest room.

1196
00:52:50,583 --> 00:52:51,823
(Our guest room)

1197
00:52:52,593 --> 00:52:53,953
- Is this the place?
- Yes.

1198
00:52:55,493 --> 00:52:57,092
- What?
- What?

1199
00:52:57,093 --> 00:52:58,423
- It just opens.
- Exactly.

1200
00:53:00,133 --> 00:53:01,332
(A romantic mood just for the two)

1201
00:53:01,333 --> 00:53:02,533
Only one bed?

1202
00:53:03,033 --> 00:53:04,162
There are two.

1203
00:53:04,163 --> 00:53:05,873
- Just next to each other.
- Joined together.

1204
00:53:06,633 --> 00:53:07,973
Even pajamas are provided.

1205
00:53:09,943 --> 00:53:15,243
(Even a jacuzzi that makes tonight all the more exciting)

1206
00:53:15,343 --> 00:53:17,683
- It's embarrassing.
- Right?

1207
00:53:17,913 --> 00:53:19,083
We're staying the night out.

1208
00:53:20,313 --> 00:53:21,782
(Embarrassed)

1209
00:53:21,783 --> 00:53:23,252
They're sharing a room...

1210
00:53:23,253 --> 00:53:24,953
just three days after meeting each other.

1211
00:53:25,523 --> 00:53:26,853
There's wine over there.

1212
00:53:26,993 --> 00:53:28,522
How about we drink a glass first?

1213
00:53:28,523 --> 00:53:29,563
I'm in. Let's do that.

1214
00:53:29,823 --> 00:53:31,793
- I can't do this in a sober state.
- Right?

1215
00:53:32,633 --> 00:53:33,633
(A small feast to enhance the mood)

1216
00:53:33,634 --> 00:53:34,692
How romantic.

1217
00:53:34,693 --> 00:53:36,632
From a jacuzzi to wine? They're going all out.

1218
00:53:36,633 --> 00:53:38,333
Gosh, I'm loving it.

1219
00:53:38,633 --> 00:53:40,233
I'll take the lead tonight.

1220
00:53:40,773 --> 00:53:42,303
- There's an opener.
- What?

1221
00:53:42,543 --> 00:53:44,142
- Cute.
- He's going to take the lead.

1222
00:53:44,143 --> 00:53:45,302
(Jun Han takes the lead with the wine opener.)

1223
00:53:45,303 --> 00:53:48,342
Noona is a Woman To Me always had an issue...

1224
00:53:48,343 --> 00:53:50,113
with that wine opener.

1225
00:53:50,213 --> 00:53:51,542
As the guys are younger,

1226
00:53:51,543 --> 00:53:52,882
can they open the wine?

1227
00:53:52,883 --> 00:53:54,512
Relatively speaking, they would have...

1228
00:53:54,513 --> 00:53:56,153
less experience opening wine bottles.

1229
00:53:56,223 --> 00:53:57,382
Are you good at opening one?

1230
00:53:57,383 --> 00:53:58,682
- What?
- Are you good at opening wine?

1231
00:53:58,683 --> 00:53:59,923
- Can you do it?
- I don't know.

1232
00:54:00,393 --> 00:54:02,053
This is how you do it, right?

1233
00:54:03,263 --> 00:54:04,293
Really.

1234
00:54:04,623 --> 00:54:06,093
- Pull them down.
- Down?

1235
00:54:07,363 --> 00:54:08,433
These right here.

1236
00:54:08,733 --> 00:54:10,302
You're right. The older woman helps.

1237
00:54:10,303 --> 00:54:11,333
Done.

1238
00:54:11,963 --> 00:54:13,002
It's my first time opening one.

1239
00:54:13,003 --> 00:54:14,303
- Seriously?
- Yes.

1240
00:54:15,703 --> 00:54:17,173
- I'll pour you a glass.
- Okay.

1241
00:54:21,543 --> 00:54:23,043
I'm really too shy right now.

1242
00:54:24,643 --> 00:54:28,453
(The overnight stay date starts with butterflies in their stomachs.)

1243
00:54:28,783 --> 00:54:30,323
What's your real ideal type?

1244
00:54:30,783 --> 00:54:31,983
- Me?
- Yes.

1245
00:54:32,453 --> 00:54:35,922
The guys I've been attracted to mostly had...

1246
00:54:35,923 --> 00:54:37,063
puppy faces.

1247
00:54:37,763 --> 00:54:38,763
That's why...

1248
00:54:38,764 --> 00:54:41,293
I'm curious about you, Jun Han.

1249
00:54:41,563 --> 00:54:44,132
You're like a big dog...

1250
00:54:44,133 --> 00:54:46,073
and yet like a Maltese.

1251
00:54:47,573 --> 00:54:49,343
What's a Maltese like?

1252
00:54:49,603 --> 00:54:50,803
A guy...

1253
00:54:51,273 --> 00:54:52,972
who likes people...

1254
00:54:52,973 --> 00:54:54,112
but is awkward...

1255
00:54:54,113 --> 00:54:57,083
because he wants to be loved.

1256
00:54:57,643 --> 00:54:59,213
It's true that I'm awkward.

1257
00:54:59,253 --> 00:55:00,583
I'm not good with girls.

1258
00:55:01,383 --> 00:55:03,583
Were you interested in me?

1259
00:55:04,353 --> 00:55:06,853
Things with Yun So seemed solid.

1260
00:55:07,223 --> 00:55:08,252
- I...
- With me?

1261
00:55:08,253 --> 00:55:11,063
Yes, you and Yun So were becoming solid.

1262
00:55:11,223 --> 00:55:12,963
That's why you were ruled out.

1263
00:55:13,963 --> 00:55:16,103
While all that happened,

1264
00:55:16,763 --> 00:55:18,433
Jin Young appeared.

1265
00:55:18,933 --> 00:55:20,833
But when she did,

1266
00:55:22,473 --> 00:55:24,402
you made me waver.

1267
00:55:24,403 --> 00:55:27,442
(You made me waver!)

1268
00:55:27,443 --> 00:55:29,212
I'm losing it.

1269
00:55:29,213 --> 00:55:31,983
You were someone out of my reach.

1270
00:55:32,513 --> 00:55:34,183
It was a surprise.

1271
00:55:34,753 --> 00:55:36,983
I did a lot of thinking while packing up.

1272
00:55:37,753 --> 00:55:39,753
(Thinking?)

1273
00:55:40,223 --> 00:55:43,823
I made up my mind to put my heart into getting to know you.

1274
00:55:44,163 --> 00:55:46,963
There's a possibility that you might find...

1275
00:55:47,193 --> 00:55:49,702
something disappointing about me as we chat.

1276
00:55:49,703 --> 00:55:51,303
I hope...

1277
00:55:51,333 --> 00:55:52,333
you don't feel...

1278
00:55:52,334 --> 00:55:53,933
any pressure.

1279
00:55:54,873 --> 00:55:56,143
I'm not.

1280
00:55:57,673 --> 00:55:59,542
We're simply getting to know each other from now on.

1281
00:55:59,543 --> 00:56:01,343
If you don't feel right, tell me.

1282
00:56:01,613 --> 00:56:02,943
- You should too.
- Okay.

1283
00:56:03,043 --> 00:56:05,643
Say that I got a chance to ask someone out.

1284
00:56:06,253 --> 00:56:08,253
I want to reset all the past situations...

1285
00:56:08,853 --> 00:56:10,222
and go on a date.

1286
00:56:10,223 --> 00:56:11,353
Same here.

1287
00:56:11,483 --> 00:56:13,453
Let's go on a separate date again.

1288
00:56:14,553 --> 00:56:15,623
Okay.

1289
00:56:15,793 --> 00:56:16,863
- I'm in.
- Pinky promise.

1290
00:56:17,223 --> 00:56:18,563
(Promising)

1291
00:56:18,663 --> 00:56:20,893
(Embarrassed)

1292
00:56:21,933 --> 00:56:23,402
I feel a bit uneasy.

1293
00:56:23,403 --> 00:56:25,432
- Ju Hee...
- Ju Hee takes things slow.

1294
00:56:25,433 --> 00:56:27,372
Calmly, slowly, and with composure.

1295
00:56:27,373 --> 00:56:28,972
Jun Han has...

1296
00:56:28,973 --> 00:56:31,773
a lot of experience dating older women.

1297
00:56:31,803 --> 00:56:33,513
- Let's give him a chance.
- Okay.

1298
00:56:34,313 --> 00:56:35,372
Nice.

1299
00:56:35,373 --> 00:56:38,042
(The two take their nice date to the jacuzzi.)

1300
00:56:38,043 --> 00:56:39,113
Cheers.

1301
00:56:39,483 --> 00:56:40,713
We look classy.

1302
00:56:42,883 --> 00:56:44,053
We look cool right now.

1303
00:56:44,853 --> 00:56:46,223
It's like a grown-up's date.

1304
00:56:48,823 --> 00:56:50,923
(Satisfied)

1305
00:56:51,063 --> 00:56:52,422
We have to wear matching PJs...

1306
00:56:52,423 --> 00:56:53,833
- to bed.
- Right.

1307
00:56:54,733 --> 00:56:56,032
I'm being completely honest.

1308
00:56:56,033 --> 00:56:57,103
It'll be my first ever time.

1309
00:56:58,303 --> 00:56:59,733
Isn't that a lot of firsts?

1310
00:57:01,333 --> 00:57:02,872
- I...
- Did you not do anything...

1311
00:57:02,873 --> 00:57:04,642
in your past relationships?

1312
00:57:04,643 --> 00:57:06,342
We rarely got matching things.

1313
00:57:06,343 --> 00:57:08,543
We never had matching PJs.

1314
00:57:11,713 --> 00:57:15,553
It doesn't seem like the kind of relationship Ju Hee wants.

1315
00:57:15,613 --> 00:57:17,252
"This is a first for me."

1316
00:57:17,253 --> 00:57:18,482
"It's giving off grown-up vibes."

1317
00:57:18,483 --> 00:57:21,022
- "We look cool." Things like that.
- Exactly.

1318
00:57:21,023 --> 00:57:23,022
I doubt Ju Hee is a fan of them.

1319
00:57:23,023 --> 00:57:24,793
Why do I feel all anxious?

1320
00:57:28,533 --> 00:57:29,732
- It's hot.
- Sorry?

1321
00:57:29,733 --> 00:57:30,903
Shall we go back inside?

1322
00:57:32,063 --> 00:57:33,473
That's a good idea.

1323
00:57:34,933 --> 00:57:37,642
There wasn't a single moment of the overnight stay date...

1324
00:57:37,643 --> 00:57:39,343
with Ju Hee that I didn't enjoy.

1325
00:57:39,573 --> 00:57:40,772
Every minute...

1326
00:57:40,773 --> 00:57:42,942
I was with her was great.

1327
00:57:42,943 --> 00:57:43,982
(The overnight date)

1328
00:57:43,983 --> 00:57:46,583
Oh, gosh. Jun Han really liked it.

1329
00:57:46,613 --> 00:57:50,623
(Do Ju Hee and Jun Han feel the same way?)

1330
00:57:50,853 --> 00:57:51,922
(Meanwhile, in Jin Young and Yun So's guest room)

1331
00:57:51,923 --> 00:57:52,992
Nice.

1332
00:57:52,993 --> 00:57:55,053
- I'm glad I won.
- Oh, my.

1333
00:57:55,623 --> 00:57:57,023
We've got a variety of drinks.

1334
00:57:59,233 --> 00:58:00,932
I'll spoil you.

1335
00:58:00,933 --> 00:58:02,133
- Go ahead.
- Thanks.

1336
00:58:02,603 --> 00:58:04,102
I get to enjoy this luxury...

1337
00:58:04,103 --> 00:58:05,603
- thanks to you.
- Right?

1338
00:58:05,933 --> 00:58:07,472
How about I dim the lights to set the mood?

1339
00:58:07,473 --> 00:58:09,032
- Sure. I was about to bring it up.
- Okay.

1340
00:58:09,033 --> 00:58:11,172
Since it's awkward, dim the lights.

1341
00:58:11,173 --> 00:58:12,202
Perfect.

1342
00:58:12,203 --> 00:58:13,742
I'm not worried about these two.

1343
00:58:13,743 --> 00:58:16,542
Jin Young gets along with others well.

1344
00:58:16,543 --> 00:58:19,753
What's more, Yun So is quite hurt.

1345
00:58:19,783 --> 00:58:21,352
I hope it gives him peace of mind.

1346
00:58:21,353 --> 00:58:22,483
What's this?

1347
00:58:23,823 --> 00:58:25,123
- How about a drink?
- I'm in.

1348
00:58:26,023 --> 00:58:28,592
Little did I think you and I would drink together...

1349
00:58:28,593 --> 00:58:30,223
all alone.

1350
00:58:31,123 --> 00:58:32,393
- Cheers first?
- Of course.

1351
00:58:32,423 --> 00:58:34,033
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

1352
00:58:35,463 --> 00:58:37,963
You must have more questions for me.

1353
00:58:38,363 --> 00:58:39,633
I do. By any chance...

1354
00:58:41,003 --> 00:58:42,533
(Hesitating)

1355
00:58:45,003 --> 00:58:46,072
- By any chance?
- By any chance,

1356
00:58:46,073 --> 00:58:47,642
is this out of revenge?

1357
00:58:47,643 --> 00:58:48,743
- No.
- No?

1358
00:58:49,243 --> 00:58:51,613
I was simply curious about you.

1359
00:58:54,253 --> 00:58:55,852
I should just quickly...

1360
00:58:55,853 --> 00:58:57,082
(Yun So talked about Ju Hee with Si Won.)

1361
00:58:57,083 --> 00:58:59,023
I feel that's the right thing to do.

1362
00:59:00,293 --> 00:59:03,223
You should consider your second choice.

1363
00:59:04,893 --> 00:59:05,963
Right.

1364
00:59:06,063 --> 00:59:07,963
Who comes to my mind right now is...

1365
00:59:08,793 --> 00:59:10,332
(Thinking)

1366
00:59:10,333 --> 00:59:11,702
Jin Young.

1367
00:59:11,703 --> 00:59:14,073
He did bring up Jin Young.

1368
00:59:14,403 --> 00:59:17,143
It's not like I chose you out of zero interest,

1369
00:59:17,603 --> 00:59:19,342
so don't get the wrong idea.

1370
00:59:19,343 --> 00:59:21,042
- Of course not.
- Don't think I chose you...

1371
00:59:21,043 --> 00:59:23,043
- because I had no other choice.
- Okay.

1372
00:59:23,783 --> 00:59:25,143
I'm glad he explained.

1373
00:59:26,153 --> 00:59:28,212
We should give each other a chance.

1374
00:59:28,213 --> 00:59:29,352
- Of course.
- Or not?

1375
00:59:29,353 --> 00:59:31,452
- Today...
- Tell me if there's no chance.

1376
00:59:31,453 --> 00:59:33,292
- You never know.
- Right.

1377
00:59:33,293 --> 00:59:35,392
I'm also human. Feelings can change.

1378
00:59:35,393 --> 00:59:36,492
- Totally.
- Right?

1379
00:59:36,493 --> 00:59:38,593
Things might change, you know?

1380
00:59:39,263 --> 00:59:42,362
Yun So looks a lot more comfortable than when he's with Ju Hee.

1381
00:59:42,363 --> 00:59:43,433
- Right?
- Yes.

1382
00:59:45,203 --> 00:59:46,233
Things are...

1383
00:59:47,303 --> 00:59:48,733
quite mixed up for me too.

1384
00:59:49,373 --> 00:59:50,473
To be frank,

1385
00:59:51,043 --> 00:59:53,643
my first choice is indeed Jun Han.

1386
00:59:54,273 --> 00:59:55,943
- What?
- Why is it "what?"

1387
00:59:56,783 --> 00:59:57,783
Earlier...

1388
00:59:57,784 --> 00:59:59,552
It's different from making me tense up.

1389
00:59:59,553 --> 01:00:01,112
- That's true.
- I feel at ease...

1390
01:00:01,113 --> 01:00:02,923
when I'm with Jun Han.

1391
01:00:03,223 --> 01:00:04,752
He's a great person as well.

1392
01:00:04,753 --> 01:00:05,823
But the thing is...

1393
01:00:07,023 --> 01:00:10,323
Since yesterday, Jeong Won has been asking...

1394
01:00:10,563 --> 01:00:12,262
if we could...

1395
01:00:12,263 --> 01:00:15,833
chat in the chat room.

1396
01:00:16,203 --> 01:00:17,502
His doing that...

1397
01:00:17,503 --> 01:00:19,002
makes me conscious of him.

1398
01:00:19,003 --> 01:00:20,003
Like, "What?"

1399
01:00:21,533 --> 01:00:22,702
As for Jun Han...

1400
01:00:22,703 --> 01:00:23,803
(But...)

1401
01:00:24,773 --> 01:00:26,973
He doesn't make me tense up.

1402
01:00:27,073 --> 01:00:29,173
Simply put, you're interested in him.

1403
01:00:30,613 --> 01:00:32,143
(Nodding)

1404
01:00:32,713 --> 01:00:34,082
(Everyone Yun So is interested in has feelings for Jun Han.)

1405
01:00:34,083 --> 01:00:36,082
- Jun Han again?
- I know, right?

1406
01:00:36,083 --> 01:00:37,723
(Upset)

1407
01:00:38,523 --> 01:00:40,193
- The pool after this glass?
- I'm in.

1408
01:00:41,593 --> 01:00:42,593
Cheers.

1409
01:00:44,323 --> 01:00:45,663
What might we do tomorrow?

1410
01:00:46,293 --> 01:00:47,393
Tomorrow?

1411
01:00:49,133 --> 01:00:52,263
I bet the women have to choose their dates.

1412
01:00:53,633 --> 01:00:55,432
Since the guys chose their dates.

1413
01:00:55,433 --> 01:00:57,042
So this time, it'll be us.

1414
01:00:57,043 --> 01:00:58,243
(The next one)

1415
01:00:59,243 --> 01:01:00,773
Will you be asking Ju Hee out...

1416
01:01:02,043 --> 01:01:03,983
on dates even from now on?

1417
01:01:04,243 --> 01:01:06,213
- Who knows?
- "Who knows?"

1418
01:01:07,913 --> 01:01:09,012
- It's okay.
- Right?

1419
01:01:09,013 --> 01:01:10,923
(Is he uncertain about Ju Hee now?)

1420
01:01:11,453 --> 01:01:13,093
I do regret one thing.

1421
01:01:14,223 --> 01:01:16,393
The moment...

1422
01:01:16,623 --> 01:01:19,093
I saw Ju Hee after moving in,

1423
01:01:19,293 --> 01:01:20,733
I withdrew from the others.

1424
01:01:20,933 --> 01:01:23,703
I found no reason to talk to others when I'd set my mind on her.

1425
01:01:26,233 --> 01:01:29,673
When Ju Hee chose Jun Han yesterday,

1426
01:01:29,803 --> 01:01:32,813
I thought, "I shouldn't have done that."

1427
01:01:34,313 --> 01:01:36,013
Should I not have ruled out the others?

1428
01:01:36,883 --> 01:01:39,043
- With how things are now...
- He can see it.

1429
01:01:39,853 --> 01:01:45,083
(Can Jin Young and Yun So become new possibilities?)

1430
01:01:50,763 --> 01:01:52,893
This is too embarrassing.

1431
01:01:53,463 --> 01:01:54,592
Why is it embarrassing?

1432
01:01:54,593 --> 01:01:55,733
Is this okay?

1433
01:01:56,603 --> 01:01:58,363
- I don't know.
- Come here?

1434
01:01:58,733 --> 01:02:00,473
No, I said, "I don't know."

1435
01:02:01,573 --> 01:02:03,042
(Tucking herself in)

1436
01:02:03,043 --> 01:02:05,172
I'm sleepy. Is it 8:30am?

1437
01:02:05,173 --> 01:02:06,743
Can I take a photo of you?

1438
01:02:07,143 --> 01:02:08,313
You look so cute.

1439
01:02:08,913 --> 01:02:10,082
- Really.
- Stop it.

1440
01:02:10,083 --> 01:02:11,283
Can I?

1441
01:02:11,843 --> 01:02:12,853
Do whatever you want.

1442
01:02:15,883 --> 01:02:17,423
- Do you want to have a look?
- Show me.

1443
01:02:18,923 --> 01:02:20,093
Show me.

1444
01:02:20,653 --> 01:02:23,063
(Close)

1445
01:02:23,993 --> 01:02:26,292
(Mischievous Yun So that's hard to see around Ju Hee)

1446
01:02:26,293 --> 01:02:28,332
Why is my face beet red?

1447
01:02:28,333 --> 01:02:30,062
It was cute. You looked like a jellyfish.

1448
01:02:30,063 --> 01:02:32,762
(The two have become much closer, thanks to the overnight stay date.)

1449
01:02:32,763 --> 01:02:34,503
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

1450
01:02:34,603 --> 01:02:35,803
Yun So...

1451
01:02:36,643 --> 01:02:38,973
seems a lot brighter right now.

1452
01:02:39,373 --> 01:02:42,513
When he's with Ju Hee, this is the only expression he has.

1453
01:02:43,483 --> 01:02:44,843
- True.
- "You're mine."

1454
01:02:45,183 --> 01:02:48,513
But right now, he's smiling and laughing.

1455
01:02:48,783 --> 01:02:51,022
We can finally see Yun So's true self.

1456
01:02:51,023 --> 01:02:52,023
- Exactly.
- I know, right?

1457
01:02:52,024 --> 01:02:54,692
He could've shown...

1458
01:02:54,693 --> 01:02:56,792
his bright side, more fitting to his age,

1459
01:02:56,793 --> 01:02:58,692
to Ju Hee.

1460
01:02:58,693 --> 01:02:59,793
Totally.

1461
01:03:00,563 --> 01:03:01,992
- Should we have snacks?
- Snacks...

1462
01:03:01,993 --> 01:03:03,432
- Snacks?
- Let's have snacks.

1463
01:03:03,433 --> 01:03:04,663
- Good idea.
- Great.

1464
01:03:05,563 --> 01:03:07,732
Things are somewhere in the middle here.

1465
01:03:07,733 --> 01:03:09,373
(Glancing)

1466
01:03:11,173 --> 01:03:13,373
We still have granola left.

1467
01:03:13,813 --> 01:03:15,543
- Is that so?
- This is mine.

1468
01:03:16,443 --> 01:03:19,812
(She keeps wandering around Si Won.)

1469
01:03:19,813 --> 01:03:21,882
Is there a need to be that close to him?

1470
01:03:21,883 --> 01:03:23,623
Ji Seung wasn't like that before.

1471
01:03:24,823 --> 01:03:25,922
- Do you need something?
- No.

1472
01:03:25,923 --> 01:03:27,293
I'm trying to see if it's here.

1473
01:03:27,993 --> 01:03:29,493
I had one of those.

1474
01:03:30,393 --> 01:03:33,493
Ji Seung must have felt a sense of danger.

1475
01:03:34,693 --> 01:03:37,663
(Meanwhile, Jin Wu, who was watching Ji Hye the whole day)

1476
01:03:38,363 --> 01:03:40,633
It's hard to sit next to you.

1477
01:03:40,733 --> 01:03:42,333
Sitting next to you is hard.

1478
01:03:42,833 --> 01:03:44,442
- Sitting next to me is hard?
- Yes.

1479
01:03:44,443 --> 01:03:45,443
Why?

1480
01:03:45,444 --> 01:03:47,473
There aren't many days when I could sit comfortably next to you.

1481
01:03:48,273 --> 01:03:49,313
How come?

1482
01:03:49,343 --> 01:03:50,412
- Sitting...
- Do you feel uncomfortable?

1483
01:03:50,413 --> 01:03:51,782
No. Whenever I take a seat,

1484
01:03:51,783 --> 01:03:53,183
we get a text to move.

1485
01:03:54,083 --> 01:03:56,012
- The timing was off?
- I'd sit down,

1486
01:03:56,013 --> 01:03:57,523
and then have to move after drawing a card.

1487
01:04:00,053 --> 01:04:01,323
Did you have bad luck?

1488
01:04:01,653 --> 01:04:03,923
I wasn't all that lucky today.

1489
01:04:04,523 --> 01:04:05,822
(Finding him cute)

1490
01:04:05,823 --> 01:04:08,363
Really, he puts things so beautifully.

1491
01:04:08,493 --> 01:04:10,062
That's how Jin Wu tells her...

1492
01:04:10,063 --> 01:04:11,862
- he was upset...
- Right.

1493
01:04:11,863 --> 01:04:13,872
- without making her feel bad.
- Exactly.

1494
01:04:13,873 --> 01:04:15,132
(Jin Wu has a different way of expressing his feelings.)

1495
01:04:15,133 --> 01:04:17,203
- You want to go, don't you?
- No, let's talk.

1496
01:04:17,573 --> 01:04:18,703
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

1497
01:04:18,973 --> 01:04:20,143
You might be tired.

1498
01:04:20,513 --> 01:04:22,043
- We were at the pool.
- Let's go.

1499
01:04:23,283 --> 01:04:26,282
(Jin Wu wants to talk alone with Ji Hye.)

1500
01:04:26,283 --> 01:04:27,582
Should we talk in your room?

1501
01:04:27,583 --> 01:04:28,713
Shall I go over right now?

1502
01:04:28,783 --> 01:04:30,283
- Let me check if it's empty.
- Okay.

1503
01:04:32,993 --> 01:04:38,763
(Jin Wu walks over, half nervous and half excited.)

1504
01:04:39,123 --> 01:04:40,532
- Ji Hye.
- Yes?

1505
01:04:40,533 --> 01:04:41,933
- Come over.
- Okay.

1506
01:04:43,763 --> 01:04:45,832
(Jin Wu finally has a chance to talk to Ji Hye alone.)

1507
01:04:45,833 --> 01:04:47,433
It's too bright in here.

1508
01:04:47,833 --> 01:04:49,173
What will they talk about?

1509
01:04:50,366 --> 01:04:52,595
(Jin Wu finally has a chance to talk to Ji Hye alone.)

1510
01:04:52,596 --> 01:04:53,896
It's too bright in here.

1511
01:04:54,496 --> 01:04:55,706
What will they talk about?

1512
01:04:57,966 --> 01:05:01,635
Listen. You and I couldn't really see each other today.

1513
01:05:01,636 --> 01:05:03,006
We took different cars.

1514
01:05:03,406 --> 01:05:05,916
So I just wanted to ask how you felt...

1515
01:05:06,416 --> 01:05:07,616
and what you did today.

1516
01:05:08,716 --> 01:05:09,986
You want to share our day?

1517
01:05:10,146 --> 01:05:13,116
Exactly. How was your day today?

1518
01:05:13,316 --> 01:05:15,856
- Jin Wu is adorable.
- We went to the pool together.

1519
01:05:16,856 --> 01:05:18,555
(Hesitating)

1520
01:05:18,556 --> 01:05:20,896
It might've just been me,

1521
01:05:21,596 --> 01:05:23,296
but we barely made eye contact.

1522
01:05:23,666 --> 01:05:24,796
Oh, no.

1523
01:05:25,836 --> 01:05:26,966
He was upset.

1524
01:05:27,436 --> 01:05:30,165
You made it quite obvious...

1525
01:05:30,166 --> 01:05:32,236
that you weren't interested in me.

1526
01:05:33,976 --> 01:05:35,746
Am I the only one who felt like that?

1527
01:05:38,046 --> 01:05:39,616
What you felt...

1528
01:05:40,476 --> 01:05:41,985
isn't all wrong.

1529
01:05:41,986 --> 01:05:43,246
Honestly,

1530
01:05:43,886 --> 01:05:46,215
I don't think it's right to make...

1531
01:05:46,216 --> 01:05:48,486
the other person confused.

1532
01:05:49,326 --> 01:05:50,426
But...

1533
01:05:51,426 --> 01:05:53,295
- I won't beat around the bush.
- No, don't.

1534
01:05:53,296 --> 01:05:54,496
I won't.

1535
01:05:55,566 --> 01:05:59,596
Right now, my first choice is...

1536
01:05:59,796 --> 01:06:00,895
- Jeong Won.
- Yes.

1537
01:06:00,896 --> 01:06:02,835
- It's Jeong Won.
- Jeong Won.

1538
01:06:02,836 --> 01:06:04,165
Yes, it's Jeong Won.

1539
01:06:04,166 --> 01:06:07,006
It's fun being with Jeong Won.

1540
01:06:07,336 --> 01:06:10,005
I like how honest Ji Hye is.

1541
01:06:10,006 --> 01:06:11,046
Right.

1542
01:06:12,676 --> 01:06:14,615
But listen, Ji Hye.

1543
01:06:14,616 --> 01:06:17,046
(Feeling bad)

1544
01:06:18,046 --> 01:06:20,116
If you're going to lie down, can't you do it on my bed?

1545
01:06:20,556 --> 01:06:21,825
Whose bed is this?

1546
01:06:21,826 --> 01:06:24,785
He's worried about her lying on another guy's bed.

1547
01:06:24,786 --> 01:06:26,526
- Isn't that cute?
- Yes, it is.

1548
01:06:26,656 --> 01:06:28,256
- Okay. Is this your bed?
- Yes.

1549
01:06:28,996 --> 01:06:30,165
And she moves for him.

1550
01:06:30,166 --> 01:06:31,666
Here's the thing. Whatever I do,

1551
01:06:32,366 --> 01:06:34,265
it won't work on you.

1552
01:06:34,266 --> 01:06:36,806
- I'm fine with that.
- Okay.

1553
01:06:37,506 --> 01:06:40,035
But you went on a date with Jeong Won yesterday.

1554
01:06:40,036 --> 01:06:41,236
True.

1555
01:06:41,606 --> 01:06:43,746
You even had a longer chat with him than with me tonight.

1556
01:06:45,006 --> 01:06:48,316
You spent much longer with him than you did with me.

1557
01:06:49,886 --> 01:06:52,116
Like how I don't know much about you,

1558
01:06:52,286 --> 01:06:54,555
you don't know much about me.

1559
01:06:54,556 --> 01:06:55,556
Yes.

1560
01:06:57,686 --> 01:06:59,095
I can also make you laugh.

1561
01:06:59,096 --> 01:07:01,226
(I can also make you laugh.)

1562
01:07:01,796 --> 01:07:04,426
That's so heartbreaking.

1563
01:07:05,096 --> 01:07:06,566
- I was like him.
- DinDin.

1564
01:07:06,696 --> 01:07:08,935
Is there hope for him? Can he make her laugh?

1565
01:07:08,936 --> 01:07:10,166
- No.
- Be honest.

1566
01:07:10,666 --> 01:07:12,005
There must be some sort of...

1567
01:07:12,006 --> 01:07:14,135
- probability.
- In that moment,

1568
01:07:14,136 --> 01:07:16,345
you must do something to make her yours,

1569
01:07:16,346 --> 01:07:17,975
so you feel like you can do anything.

1570
01:07:17,976 --> 01:07:20,575
But you don't have what she wants.

1571
01:07:20,576 --> 01:07:21,576
You just don't.

1572
01:07:22,086 --> 01:07:23,916
(Upset)

1573
01:07:24,216 --> 01:07:25,585
I can also make you laugh.

1574
01:07:25,586 --> 01:07:27,686
(It's not only Jeong Won who can make you laugh.)

1575
01:07:28,256 --> 01:07:29,685
(How cute.)

1576
01:07:29,686 --> 01:07:31,995
Just seeing her laugh is enough to make you happy.

1577
01:07:31,996 --> 01:07:34,455
We have plenty of time. We can go on more dates.

1578
01:07:34,456 --> 01:07:36,166
That's why, thinking that...

1579
01:07:37,096 --> 01:07:38,995
I'm already not an option for you...

1580
01:07:38,996 --> 01:07:41,096
- You don't want me to do that?
- No.

1581
01:07:42,566 --> 01:07:44,536
But like I said yesterday,

1582
01:07:45,736 --> 01:07:46,736
you don't have to be sorry.

1583
01:07:46,737 --> 01:07:48,436
That's just how you feel.

1584
01:07:50,546 --> 01:07:52,646
But when I look at you...

1585
01:07:53,046 --> 01:07:54,216
I'm looking at you too?

1586
01:07:54,446 --> 01:07:56,886
It's either that or you look upset.

1587
01:07:57,316 --> 01:07:59,155
Right, I'm not very strong-minded,

1588
01:07:59,156 --> 01:08:00,156
so my emotions show on my face.

1589
01:08:00,157 --> 01:08:01,715
Yes, and that's why...

1590
01:08:01,716 --> 01:08:03,686
it's hard for me to look at you.

1591
01:08:05,256 --> 01:08:08,125
Whether it's Jeong Won or someone else,

1592
01:08:08,126 --> 01:08:11,096
when you're having fun with another person,

1593
01:08:11,726 --> 01:08:14,366
obviously I wouldn't feel great.

1594
01:08:14,696 --> 01:08:16,605
But something like that...

1595
01:08:16,606 --> 01:08:19,035
isn't enough to make me give up on...

1596
01:08:19,036 --> 01:08:20,176
my feelings for you.

1597
01:08:23,276 --> 01:08:26,346
When someone like Jin Wu enters his 30s...

1598
01:08:26,846 --> 01:08:28,686
- He's going to be really popular.
- He's a real gem.

1599
01:08:29,746 --> 01:08:30,816
I see myself in him.

1600
01:08:31,286 --> 01:08:32,355
What?

1601
01:08:32,356 --> 01:08:33,715
(The buildup is insane.)

1602
01:08:33,716 --> 01:08:35,485
He's like me in 2007.

1603
01:08:35,486 --> 01:08:36,826
(He's like DinDin in 2007.)

1604
01:08:38,456 --> 01:08:39,855
You're bold, though.

1605
01:08:39,856 --> 01:08:41,896
You're really direct about your feelings.

1606
01:08:42,326 --> 01:08:44,696
Yes, holding back on it...

1607
01:08:45,536 --> 01:08:46,865
- wouldn't do me any good.
- You really don't hold back...

1608
01:08:46,866 --> 01:08:48,196
on how you feel.

1609
01:08:48,966 --> 01:08:51,805
I know it's not easy to say all this.

1610
01:08:51,806 --> 01:08:53,336
Of course.

1611
01:08:53,536 --> 01:08:54,935
He's really brave.

1612
01:08:54,936 --> 01:08:57,446
I don't know about other people, but to me it's easy.

1613
01:08:57,646 --> 01:08:59,375
- Really?
- This is the only way I know.

1614
01:08:59,376 --> 01:09:00,916
- Really?
- Yes, this is all I know.

1615
01:09:02,046 --> 01:09:04,086
You're really brave.

1616
01:09:10,056 --> 01:09:11,886
- Is this hand cream?
- Yes, you can use it.

1617
01:09:12,596 --> 01:09:13,696
How do I open this?

1618
01:09:14,726 --> 01:09:16,565
If you had asked me if I was cold today,

1619
01:09:16,566 --> 01:09:17,966
I would open this for you.

1620
01:09:18,596 --> 01:09:19,696
How do I open this?

1621
01:09:20,196 --> 01:09:22,066
He complained for one second and opened it for her right away.

1622
01:09:22,606 --> 01:09:23,805
Wouldn't it be better to apply it on the back of your hand?

1623
01:09:23,806 --> 01:09:24,966
He's cute.

1624
01:09:25,036 --> 01:09:28,136
Jin Wu probably felt butterflies just from holding her hand.

1625
01:09:31,506 --> 01:09:33,116
I'm curious.

1626
01:09:33,716 --> 01:09:34,976
Jeong Won is your top choice.

1627
01:09:35,346 --> 01:09:37,145
Does that mean everyone else is irrelevant?

1628
01:09:37,146 --> 01:09:39,356
Or am I your second choice?

1629
01:09:40,156 --> 01:09:41,885
No, there are other people besides Jeong Won.

1630
01:09:41,886 --> 01:09:44,556
I don't know how this sounds to you,

1631
01:09:44,626 --> 01:09:46,426
but I'm going to go on a date with Jun Han...

1632
01:09:46,956 --> 01:09:48,456
and I'm going to go on a date with Si Won.

1633
01:09:50,626 --> 01:09:52,265
- I see.
- Yes, I'm going to go on dates.

1634
01:09:52,266 --> 01:09:53,596
Goodness.

1635
01:09:54,896 --> 01:09:56,366
I'm asking if I'm currently second choice to you.

1636
01:09:57,606 --> 01:09:59,906
I'm going to decide after talking to everyone at least once.

1637
01:10:02,846 --> 01:10:04,405
You're hard to read, Ji Hye.

1638
01:10:04,406 --> 01:10:05,645
- Me?
- You're hard to read.

1639
01:10:05,646 --> 01:10:06,675
How am I hard to read?

1640
01:10:06,676 --> 01:10:07,776
I don't know. You're hard to read.

1641
01:10:07,846 --> 01:10:08,846
- Me?
- Yes.

1642
01:10:08,847 --> 01:10:11,146
I'm as simple as it gets. I just say everything as it is.

1643
01:10:13,616 --> 01:10:14,916
I don't know right now.

1644
01:10:16,156 --> 01:10:17,486
- What?
- You're hard to read.

1645
01:10:18,456 --> 01:10:20,855
It's because things aren't going...

1646
01:10:20,856 --> 01:10:22,626
the way Jin Wu wanted. That's why she's hard to read.

1647
01:10:25,066 --> 01:10:26,896
But it's obvious to anyone watching from the outside.

1648
01:10:27,896 --> 01:10:30,435
(Tonight, it feels hard to win her heart.)

1649
01:10:30,436 --> 01:10:31,636
Gosh, it's hard.

1650
01:10:33,276 --> 01:10:35,335
Don't come inside our room. It might be messy.

1651
01:10:35,336 --> 01:10:36,876
That's because we didn't bring much.

1652
01:10:37,406 --> 01:10:38,646
This part is important.

1653
01:10:38,976 --> 01:10:40,146
It's very important.

1654
01:10:41,246 --> 01:10:44,416
(How will this conversation go?)

1655
01:10:44,846 --> 01:10:45,886
This is how I feel.

1656
01:10:46,586 --> 01:10:50,485
When we went on our first date, we talked a lot in the car.

1657
01:10:50,486 --> 01:10:53,626
- When we talked then, - Yes.

1658
01:10:54,956 --> 01:10:57,465
you said that you would talk to 2 to 3 people you're attracted to...

1659
01:10:57,466 --> 01:10:59,766
- and then go all in on one person.
- Right.

1660
01:11:01,496 --> 01:11:02,966
How many people are you attracted to?

1661
01:11:03,736 --> 01:11:06,706
I think what counts as attraction...

1662
01:11:07,376 --> 01:11:08,976
is unclear for me.

1663
01:11:09,106 --> 01:11:11,075
Because I haven’t talked to them at all yet.

1664
01:11:11,076 --> 01:11:12,746
- Right.
- Yes.

1665
01:11:12,916 --> 01:11:15,716
Are you the type who has to get to know people individually?

1666
01:11:16,886 --> 01:11:21,056
That's why I thought you would see this...

1667
01:11:21,756 --> 01:11:24,626
as a time to get to know the other younger men.

1668
01:11:25,796 --> 01:11:26,896
He remembered.

1669
01:11:27,426 --> 01:11:28,496
Yes.

1670
01:11:29,766 --> 01:11:31,126
Yesterday,

1671
01:11:31,496 --> 01:11:33,095
I didn't really talk to people...

1672
01:11:33,096 --> 01:11:34,366
aside from you.

1673
01:11:34,566 --> 01:11:35,566
- That's right.
- Yes.

1674
01:11:35,606 --> 01:11:37,736
That's why I sent my Love QR message to you.

1675
01:11:38,366 --> 01:11:40,376
- I know. I didn't send one to you.
- Yes.

1676
01:11:40,436 --> 01:11:41,436
That's okay.

1677
01:11:41,437 --> 01:11:43,375
That's why...

1678
01:11:43,376 --> 01:11:44,945
- But I regretted it immediately.
- I took it as that.

1679
01:11:44,946 --> 01:11:46,145
- Really?
- Yes.

1680
01:11:46,146 --> 01:11:48,416
That you were getting to know different people.

1681
01:11:48,476 --> 01:11:51,416
Anyway, the Love QR message I sent to someone else was meaningless.

1682
01:11:51,786 --> 01:11:54,186
I did choose you for the First Impression Vote...

1683
01:11:54,556 --> 01:11:57,085
and we had a good date.

1684
01:11:57,086 --> 01:11:59,526
You're the person I've talked to the most.

1685
01:12:00,996 --> 01:12:03,566
If it weren't for today's game, I would still be confused.

1686
01:12:03,796 --> 01:12:04,926
- Really?
- Yes.

1687
01:12:06,366 --> 01:12:07,765
That's right. I don't think...

1688
01:12:07,766 --> 01:12:10,005
I'm that easy to read.

1689
01:12:10,006 --> 01:12:11,106
You're good at hiding your feelings.

1690
01:12:13,536 --> 01:12:15,675
- You're good at it.
- People usually can't tell.

1691
01:12:15,676 --> 01:12:17,706
- Really?
- Yes, I'm not sure why.

1692
01:12:19,076 --> 01:12:20,245
(Ji Seung opened up about her feelings for the first time.)

1693
01:12:20,246 --> 01:12:21,445
There's that.

1694
01:12:21,446 --> 01:12:22,585
(Ji Seung opened up about her feelings for the first time.)

1695
01:12:22,586 --> 01:12:26,255
I get it when you tell me directly.

1696
01:12:26,256 --> 01:12:27,256
Right.

1697
01:12:27,257 --> 01:12:30,185
But the Love QR message is still a choice,

1698
01:12:30,186 --> 01:12:32,026
so I'm sorry that I didn't send it to you.

1699
01:12:35,056 --> 01:12:36,926
There's no need to be sorry.

1700
01:12:38,266 --> 01:12:41,266
Just express as much as you can here.

1701
01:12:41,696 --> 01:12:42,936
That's all.

1702
01:12:45,606 --> 01:12:47,236
There's really no need to be sorry.

1703
01:12:50,676 --> 01:12:52,245
To be honest, Ji Seung is free...

1704
01:12:52,246 --> 01:12:54,915
to send her Love QR message to anyone she wants.

1705
01:12:54,916 --> 01:12:56,085
There's no reason for her to apologize.

1706
01:12:56,086 --> 01:12:58,246
Yes, Si Won is right.

1707
01:12:59,016 --> 01:13:01,156
- Right?
- I guess.

1708
01:13:02,456 --> 01:13:04,925
We thought the women will get to choose our dates,

1709
01:13:04,926 --> 01:13:06,296
and I thought it was going to be today.

1710
01:13:06,356 --> 01:13:08,196
Is she going to bring it up?

1711
01:13:08,356 --> 01:13:10,426
What if I don't get to choose first?

1712
01:13:10,726 --> 01:13:11,966
If you don't?

1713
01:13:12,536 --> 01:13:14,866
Even if I don't, I want you to know how I feel.

1714
01:13:15,736 --> 01:13:16,766
Gosh.

1715
01:13:18,006 --> 01:13:19,975
Okay. Are you tired?

1716
01:13:19,976 --> 01:13:21,075
- What?
- Are you tired?

1717
01:13:21,076 --> 01:13:22,776
- No, I'm okay.
- You sure?

1718
01:13:23,376 --> 01:13:24,376
Yes.

1719
01:13:25,506 --> 01:13:26,975
This is so funny.

1720
01:13:26,976 --> 01:13:29,745
If you didn't tell me, I don't think I would've known how you feel.

1721
01:13:29,746 --> 01:13:31,685
Of course not. He would have never known.

1722
01:13:31,686 --> 01:13:33,455
That's why you should say how you feel.

1723
01:13:33,456 --> 01:13:34,915
Yes.

1724
01:13:34,916 --> 01:13:36,485
(Embarrassed)

1725
01:13:36,486 --> 01:13:37,726
Right.

1726
01:13:38,056 --> 01:13:40,895
I'm glad that everyone saw me in a good light...

1727
01:13:40,896 --> 01:13:42,226
with the rugby game.

1728
01:13:42,666 --> 01:13:45,365
Right, the other women were thrilled about you.

1729
01:13:45,366 --> 01:13:46,765
I didn't get to see your back closely.

1730
01:13:46,766 --> 01:13:47,896
- You didn't?
- No.

1731
01:13:48,296 --> 01:13:50,536
Earlier in the car, I felt that Ji Hye...

1732
01:13:51,536 --> 01:13:53,006
and Yu Jin...

1733
01:13:53,876 --> 01:13:56,605
were trying to talk to me...

1734
01:13:56,606 --> 01:13:58,746
and initiate conversation.

1735
01:13:59,676 --> 01:14:01,146
- At least, from my perspective.
- Yu Jin?

1736
01:14:01,376 --> 01:14:04,515
No, Yu Jin just likes to talk.

1737
01:14:04,516 --> 01:14:06,816
- Right.
- She likes to talk.

1738
01:14:07,086 --> 01:14:09,925
(What?)

1739
01:14:09,926 --> 01:14:12,155
Hey, let's calm down.

1740
01:14:12,156 --> 01:14:13,325
She doesn't know how old she is,

1741
01:14:13,326 --> 01:14:14,856
but she treated her as someone older than her.

1742
01:14:17,066 --> 01:14:20,036
No, Yu Jin just likes to talk.

1743
01:14:20,136 --> 01:14:22,505
- Right.
- She likes to talk.

1744
01:14:22,506 --> 01:14:24,236
Wait.

1745
01:14:25,206 --> 01:14:26,936
Wasn't drinking a shot together with arms linked for your second choice?

1746
01:14:28,276 --> 01:14:30,246
- Yes.
- It means I was the second choice.

1747
01:14:32,106 --> 01:14:33,216
Who was your first choice?

1748
01:14:33,916 --> 01:14:34,976
My first choice?

1749
01:14:35,146 --> 01:14:38,185
You know I thought about it a lot.

1750
01:14:38,186 --> 01:14:40,316
- Yes.
- It's because...

1751
01:14:41,086 --> 01:14:42,885
I didn't get a Love QR message from you yesterday...

1752
01:14:42,886 --> 01:14:45,826
and you're getting to know other people.

1753
01:14:46,556 --> 01:14:49,365
And, of course, it's not that I'm not attracted at all.

1754
01:14:49,366 --> 01:14:50,866
(Si Won dodged the question about his first choice.)

1755
01:14:53,236 --> 01:14:54,336
That's it.

1756
01:14:57,536 --> 01:14:59,635
(Where will Ji Seung and Si Won's hearts go?)

1757
01:14:59,636 --> 01:15:00,906
They're back where they started.

1758
01:15:03,046 --> 01:15:04,805
(The mailbox is filling up with cards about...)

1759
01:15:04,806 --> 01:15:06,576
(about the hidden charms of the younger men.)

1760
01:15:06,976 --> 01:15:09,315
(Random Charm Card Date: Read the charm cards about...)

1761
01:15:09,316 --> 01:15:11,386
(the younger men together and each pick one.)

1762
01:15:12,137 --> 01:15:15,536
(The older women's subtle competition...)

1763
01:15:15,537 --> 01:15:18,947
(for a date with the younger man they want)

1764
01:15:19,677 --> 01:15:23,977
(A fateful encounter decided by a single card)

1765
01:15:25,017 --> 01:15:29,357
(The older women are surprised by the unexpected results.)

1766
01:15:29,787 --> 01:15:31,116
(I think today is the beginning.)

1767
01:15:31,117 --> 01:15:32,586
I love this.

1768
01:15:32,587 --> 01:15:34,156
"Is this getting romantic?"

1769
01:15:34,157 --> 01:15:36,127
That's the heart-fluttered feeling I get.

1770
01:15:36,827 --> 01:15:38,897
I loved every moment we spent together.

1771
01:15:39,067 --> 01:15:41,267
I got to see another charming side of him.

1772
01:15:44,267 --> 01:15:46,506
(Would you like to extend your current date?)

1773
01:15:46,507 --> 01:15:49,007
(Or would you like to go on a date with a different younger man?)

1774
01:15:49,477 --> 01:15:51,606
(The text was only sent to the older women,)

1775
01:15:51,607 --> 01:15:53,777
(making the younger men nervous.)

1776
01:15:55,077 --> 01:15:59,547
(Will the older women extend their date?)

1777
01:16:00,087 --> 01:16:02,457
(The women's choices are unpredictable.)

1778
01:16:02,887 --> 01:16:04,817
Gosh, this is wrong.

1779
01:16:05,217 --> 01:16:06,827
(I was genuinely shocked.)

1780
01:16:07,387 --> 01:16:11,457
(Everyone is shocked by the result.)

1781
01:16:12,997 --> 01:16:15,467
(Well, look at this.)

1782
01:16:16,537 --> 01:16:17,837
(I was annoyed.)

1783
01:16:18,437 --> 01:16:19,866
(The dates were meant to be exciting.)

1784
01:16:19,867 --> 01:16:21,167
(But what awaits at the end?)
